<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=1959&amp;p=9882#p9882"><![CDATA[
Right click the Start button -&gt; Settings to open Classic Start Menu settings. In the search box of the settings, type: screen and check the option: &quot;Show Start screen shortcut&quot;.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Fri Jan 03, 2014 8:35 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
